    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 (FD3S) in collector-grade condition. This specimen retains the original 13B-REW twin-rotor power plant featuring its factory-spec sequential twin-turbocharger configuration. The drivetrain is immaculate, delivering linear boost across the RPM range with a crisp 5-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full cooling system refresh with a multi-core aluminum radiator and a comprehensive vacuum line 'rat's nest' replacement using high-temp silicone to ensure solenoid reliability. Compression test results are optimal across all rotor faces, verifying the integrity of the apex seals. The chassis remains taut, riding on its original four-wheel double-wishbone suspension with no subframe corrosion or bushing fatigue. Purely OEM mechanical excellence.",
